OL,3,CWhen five became one: Spice Girls mark
OL,4,C30 years since band auditions with
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FThe Spice Girls have unearthed footage
OL,8,Fto celebrate 30 years since their
OL,9,Ffirst auditions.
OL,11,FThe group, which formed in 1994, went
OL,12,Fon to dominate the charts with hits
OL,13,Fsuch as Wannabe, Who Do You Think You
OL,14,FAre?, 2 Become 1 and Viva Forever.
OL,16,FA video released to mark the occasion
OL,17,Fshows band members Emma Bunton,
OL,18,FVictoria Adams (now Beckham), Geri
OL,19,FHalliwell, Mel Brown and Mel Chisholm
OL,20,Fdancing and messing around together.
