OL,3,CWhen five became one: Spice Girls mark
OL,4,C30 years since band auditions with
OL,5,Cvideo
OL,7,FA post on X said: "Today marks the
OL,8,F30th anniversary of the very first
OL,9,FSpice Girls auditions!
OL,11,F"What started back in 1994 has turned
OL,12,Finto an amazing journey, way beyond
OL,13,Fanything we could have ever imagined.
OL,15,F"Thank you to our fans for your
OL,16,Fsupport from day one.
OL,17,F_FriendshipNeverEnds."
OL,19,FThe group are dressed down, with
OL,20,FAdams, now Beckham, in a red Adidas t-
OL,21,Fshirt and belted jeans.
