OL,7,FIn one clip, Chisholm sports a
OL,8,Fbackwards baseball cap and Bunton
OL,9,Fwears a Tweetie Pie t-shirt.
OL,11,FFans of the band, will also be able to
OL,12,Fslam stamps down and wind them all
OL,13,Faround after Royal Mail announced
OL,15,FThe release marks the first time Royal
OL,16,FMail has dedicated an entire stamp
OL,17,Fissue to a female pop group.
OL,19,FAll the members of the girl group
OL,20,Fexcept Beckham reunited in 2019 for a
OL,21,Ftour of the UK and Ireland.
